<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und recht von ir
                                    <expan>gepot<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, ee sie uns entsagt
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan></add>. Dewcht in
